2026-05-19T05:34:09.1753036Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-19T05:34:09.1753396Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-19T05:34:09.1753633Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-19T05:34:09.1754033Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-19T05:34:09.1754392Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-19T05:34:09.1754733Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
